{"tid":831833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳帆：千五宗塌樹衝擊大　發展局：近萬五宗塌樹報告","createTime":"2018-09-22T10:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T14:53:37.000Z","uid":41404,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8072f9ff1f147618107f0501272f8b1157f534c9","tid":831833,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:01:36.000Z","msg":"陳帆：千五宗塌樹衝擊大　發展局：近萬五宗塌樹報告　<br />\n2018-09-22 HKT 16:47<br />\n<br />\n運輸及房屋局局長陳帆表示，山竹吹襲香港造成的塌樹問題，對香港衝擊好大，過去一個星期已接獲1500宗報告關於塌樹，派出600人清理樹木，會優先處理主要幹道、會影響學童上課、衞生情況的地方。<br />\n<br />\n發展局下午回覆查詢時表示，截至9月18日，共收到的塌樹報告共14799 宗，另外政府昨晚的新聞稿指出，康文署轄下約有1萬7千棵樹木在颱風期間被強風吹倒，需要移除。<br />\n<br />\n本台再向陳帆新聞秘書查詢，陳帆提及的塌樹報告，與其他政府部門提供的數字有出入，新聞秘書回覆時表示，陳帆所提及的是清除塌樹報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1419459-20180922.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1419459-20180922.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ApFr65%2F7CQXVI7Zo3g%2FMeQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e5b4113e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1419459-20180922.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f3616e2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1419459-20180922.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d02c5f63616e9eb0825560cf8178c97cbf6fa3d1","tid":831833,"uid":922,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:04:35.000Z","msg":"條友訓撚醒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7da1ed74721170454c5a27b59d86e0872c7a1d3","tid":831833,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:05:33.000Z","msg":"地球真係好危險"},{"pid":"768ba4065537c933d6919caf409e9e39175d1e67","tid":831833,"uid":39200,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:06:13.000Z","msg":"個腦剩係得條廢鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8163924151950f47a761884b560243ff7c34821e","tid":